<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8"/>
    <title>Top of the Poops - Support, Sponsor or Subscribe</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Analysing sewage dumps by water companies in the UK">

    {{> chunks/favicons }}
    {{> chunks/meta-styles }}
    {{> chunks/meta-scripts }}

    {{> components/meta-opengraph
            title="Support & Subscriptions"
            twitterImageUri=share.twitterImageUri
    }}

    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
</head>
<body>
{{> chunks/navbar }}

{{#> components/jumbotron }}
    We need your support
{{/components/jumbotron}}

<script async
        src="https://js.stripe.com/v3/buy-button.js">
</script>


<div class="container">

    <div class="row justify-content-md-center">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <p>Running a website with this much information in it costs money - Running the servers, design and programming are all expensive. Your support
            means we can develop more information sources - start to personalise the information - develop pollution notification services, and generally improve
                the quality and relevance of our information.</p>
            <p>If you can, please support us with either a one-off or small recurring subscription - which you can cancel with no notice at any time.</p>
            <p>We won't add you to any mailing lists</p>
            <p>Thank you!</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col mb-3">
            <div class="card h-100 text-center">
                <div class="card-header">Stripe</div>
                <div class="events  card-body">

                    With Stripe you can subscribe as a Top-of-the-Poops supporter. It's a small monthly subscription, you can cancel at any time. You don't need to share any information with us.

                    <stripe-buy-button
                            buy-button-id="buy_btn_1PuHaFI1rZXPCk5qWxlwBBIb"
                            publishable-key="pk_live_51PuHKQI1rZXPCk5q9GUWxgUcSqKzIDqeo9JK7wFDjZwVKKcwks3PKCSJix9zbevhuhggUUHR9DiEmXdKDk1nqRNy00Ko01Hebm"
                    >
                    </stripe-buy-button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col mb-3">
            <div class="card h-100 text-center">
                <div class="card-header">GoFundMe</div>
                <div class="events card-body">

                    GoFundMe allows you to send a one-off payment to help support our work. It's quick and easy.

                    {{> components/gofundme text="Support on GoFundMe"}}
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col  mb-3">
            <div class="card h-100 text-center">
                <div class="card-header">GitHub Sponsor</div>
                <div class="events  card-body">

                    For the techies, GitHub Sponsors allows people with a GitHub account or organisation to sponsor our Open Source technology.

                    <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/sponsors/top-poop">
                        <button class="btn btn-warning mt-2" aria-label="Sponsor @top-poop on GitHub">
                            <svg aria-hidden="true" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16"
                                 data-view-component="true"
                                 class="octicon octicon-heart icon-sponsor color-fg-sponsors me-2">
